{"tid":214360,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"[RIP]皇室堡械劫案主腦病逝","createTime":"2017-04-23T17:17:18.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-24T00:53:40.000Z","uid":9962,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"0ce0b8f4e6f7649e41619bfd5d3877376ad9e7f4","tid":214360,"uid":9962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T17:17:18.000Z","msg":"當年轟動一時嘅皇室堡4樓械劫案，隨著主腦「湖南佬」的病逝終於曲終人散。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/04/24/004823_aa43d495b6b8c16e7b73363b526ea743.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F04%2F24%2F004823_aa43d495b6b8c16e7b73363b526ea743.jpg&h=c35a4fc4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n（械劫案主腦「湖南佬」-曾守明飾）<br />\n據一位身材及智商都不合格的中国特務透露，「湖南佬」係來自洞庭湖草頭鄉上楊村。兩人於一間餐廳內因一口濃痰而結識，更有「他鄉遇故知」的感覺（示意圖）<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/snn790p.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fsnn790p.jpg&h=e110ed91&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n可惜世事往往出人意表，當年的鄉里今天竟然要親手制服<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/04/24/005421_5935d59e2647586873b1693f789b2bee.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F04%2F24%2F005421_5935d59e2647586873b1693f789b2bee.jpg&h=8dfe4ee6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n當年死者包括：金舖怕痛男職員、女學生及德仔老竇<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TL3S9XV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTL3S9XV.jpg&h=00e03702&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n資深男藝員-曾守明先生 一路好走 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/04/24/011554_baff45e32f7f14ee5a2775f73be43560.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F04%2F24%2F011554_baff45e32f7f14ee5a2775f73be43560.jpg&h=aed4e78a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e3c422864dc89a84e9e068c8d14d72e169713784","tid":214360,"uid":20943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T17:22:34.000Z","msg":"Rip<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nGoogle先知原來係真"},{"pid":"3d9ca139e1b7a266f8309d7b3f0ee97dcc7812f0","tid":214360,"uid":23829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T17:25:20.000Z","msg":"單案當年好哄動 有成個月屋企唔俾我出街玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e415714b62383492a6847f52bb6ce7f2a1f5311f","tid":214360,"uid":9962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T17:27:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>單案當年好哄動 有成個月屋企唔俾我出街玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n細個成日都去皇室堡附近行街，突然有一日屋企人唔再帶我去.. <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2345f248aa1619af737720cdb0851bd7fe70ea99","tid":214360,"uid":17928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T17:34:46.000Z","msg":"德仔老豆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59fde96263edbe7a7c58a928a19862643e94e0a2","tid":214360,"uid":97465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T17:36:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>德仔老豆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n認錯人啦清"},{"pid":"b6ef6d94f9711b1f0fb33bd3492a80d72129b42b","tid":214360,"uid":9962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-24T00:17:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>德仔老豆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n當年有個有心人定無名氏拎左$500帛金去報館<br />\n#催淚"},{"pid":"f689e92c29b5d36f91a619248c02f6eb360a1be7","tid":214360,"uid":49,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-24T00:45:51.000Z","msg":"Rip<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"334fe468f4a0354e781ab8065a6bcd5